{
  "stem": "24409.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was two organizations, which were actually one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were not actually one, because I was not under the command of the center in London, or in Paris.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did it-- I had some trouble with them, because of this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they wanted me to go, and to discuss everything with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, no, [? maybe ?] I cannot do it, to give account what's happened to the money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't write down that-- it's worth nothing to you, anyhow, because how do you know that I gave this guy 50 pounds, or 5 pounds as a bribe?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't have the time to write down, in the evening, what I spend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were two organizations, but still working very closely together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had been pressured by Eichmann to leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Eichmann had told them, he said, don't leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Within a very short time, three days or so, and they all go to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I called Mendler and told him, I would have a ship.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I don't have the money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can't do anything for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, how much do you need?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, 2,000 pounds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He says, I have them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was ready to sit down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You have 2,000 pounds, yes?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "How do you get that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't ask him how he got them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I found out later that he got official permission of the Czech puppet government, with agreement of the Germans, to transfer Czech crowns into pounds, so and so much for each immigrant.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When Hitler invaded Czechoslovakia, already when he made us to take [INAUDIBLE], a fund was established-- I think it was $10 million-- to help with immigration.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
